Custom Cinnamon Menu applet ToDo list:
 [ ] **Make the list of recently executed applications global:** Currently, the list of recently executed applications (**Recent applications** category) is stored in a per applet manner. If there are various menu applets placed in different panels, each of them will have its own list of recent applications and each of those lists will be different.

